    "patch_code": "public static <B extends T> Class<B> fooBar (B bar){\n\n\t\tif(_class==bar.getClass())return (Class<B>)_class;\n\t\t\n\t\tif(!bar.getClass().isAssignableFrom(_class))throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"klasa nie jest podtypem\");\n        \n\t\t// sprawdzamy czy ma rodzica i wywolujemy recursive na klasie rodzica, poki nie dostaniemy Class<T>\n\t\t\t\tif(fooBar((T)bar.getParent()))return fooBar((T)bar.getParent());\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tfor(int i = 0; i < ((CtClassImpl)bar.getClass()).getInterfaces().length;i++){\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t   if(fooBar((T)((CtClassImpl)bar.getClass()).getInterfaces()[i]))return fooBar((T)((CtClassImpl)bar.getClass()).getInterfaces()[i]);\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\treturn (Class<B>)bar.getClass();\n\n};",
